Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}一路前行至今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.26,0:01:12.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}并不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:18.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}只是偶尔会犯错会跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}盲目去追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}明知在勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:27.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}都只为遵守无声的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:30.20,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}不想当任风摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:32.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}静静流动的云彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:37.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}将过去曾经发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}想要超越的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}默默地留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:46.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}别灰心 别后悔Yeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3\c&H4134AB&}on the way to GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:51.11,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}这条路有无限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.11,0:01:55.63,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}脚踏实地比大步迈进更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:57.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3\c&H4134AB&}on the way to GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路上即使是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:04.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\be3}只要笑着一定会传达给谁
